				<td colspan="2"><span>There was a good post in the LDoN topic that talked about this in detail.  
<br />

<br />
For me in an LDoN group, I will (usually) twist largos, verus of victory, chorus of clarity and niv's.  These are all sung songs.
<br />

<br />
So, when I pull with snare, on the way back in I sing amplification, then do a 4 twist and, depending upon what is happening, let amp drop and keep twisting or twist it in again.
<br />

<br />
If you think about amp giving a plus 80% to all those effects (except haste), I think it is worth it.
<br />

