			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Back when Cassindra's Chant and Chorus of Clarity were instant, singing mods would affect the amount of mana the song would give. At about the time the Rathe event was first beaten, the devs believed that a single bard putting out 60~ mana per tick was probably a bit much, and so nerf the songs to the regen form they are now. They are no longer affected by modifiers.
